import React from "react";
import {
    NavLink
} from 'react-router-dom';


function Menu(props) {
    return ( <
        nav className = "deep-green" >
        <
        ul >
        <
        li className = "Menu-list Logo" > Quteba < /li>

        <
        li className = "Menu-list" >
        <
        NavLink to = "/"
        activeClassName = "is-active"
        exact = {
            true
        } > Home < /NavLink> <
        a className = "Menu-link"
        href = "#" > Home < /a> <
        /li > <
        li className = "Menu-list" >
        <
        a className = "Menu-link"
        href = "#" > About < /a> <
        /li > <
        li className = "Menu-list" >
        <
        a className = "Menu-link"
        href = "#" > Contact < /a> <
        /li > <
        /ul> <
        /nav >
    );
}

export default Menu;
